				<strong class="title">General Comment</strong>This song is not a song with lots of lairs... It is not about something christian or anything symbolic... Dont let his metaphors fool you, it is a plain and beautiful love song... Where Dylan looks back at when he met Sara, and the feeling of security that she gave him from all the mad things happening in the world and in his life at the time...				
